<p>France<br/>End of April</p>
<p>Dear Tommy<br/>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Just a line to break the sad news of Dean's death, he was shot thro the heart with a machine gun bullet on the hop over about a fortnight ago, death was instantaneous [indecipherable] I will send you &ndash;a location of his grave.  I can see the Captn &amp; get them to allow me to send it to you. Another old friend of mine Phil Williams who was in the same position as Dean &amp; his brother being  killed on Gallopli. Things are pretty right here at</p>
